archimate:BusinessProcess.name: Deliver Program/Project Methodologies & Support
archimate:BusinessProcess.documentation: Document the program and project methodologies to be used by all projects within the enterprise, and provide documentation templates and any project management tools required. Note that projects are actually managed within other areas of the enterprise but follow the guidelines defined by this process, which provides a template for specific applications of Program & Project Management in any area of the enterprise.
